Info
----

The replace controller role that implements this: https://access.redhat.com/documentation/en-us/red_hat_openstack_platform/13/html/director_installation_and_usage/sect-scaling_the_overcloud#sect-Replacing_Controller_Nodes

Supported product versions:
    - OSP13
    - OSP14


Pre-requirements
----------------
1. Gather facts for hypervisor::

    - name: Gather facts for Hypervisor
      hosts: hypervisor
      gather_facts: yes
      any_errors_fatal: true